snippet.title: Distance - The Creativity Update
snippet.description:
STEAM: http://store.steampowered.com/app/233610
TWITTER: https://twitter.com/refractstudios
FACEBOOK: https://facebook.com/refractstudios
MUSIC: "Even Deeper into the Void" by http://twitter.com/torcht

The Creativity Update is now available on Steam and Humble! It includes 3 new levels, a new ability, improved camera, Oculus Rift CV1 support, new editor tools, and more!

Read the full announcement + changelog here:
http://steamcommunity.com/games/distance/announcements/detail/806519864418621904
